dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Orestimba Peak and Newman quadrangles, Merced and Stanislaus Counties, California
dct_alternative_sm: Geology Orestimba Peak and Newman quadrangle
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Orestimba Peak, CA 1953 photorevised 1971, AMS 1758 I SW -- Series V895; Newman, CA 1952, photorevised 1971, photoinspected 1978. DMA 1758 I SE -- series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
Includes "pertinent references", most recent published in 1964.
